<p><strong>[1] </strong>Players registered to the community are not allowed to play in a league, or a tournament that the community is participating, in unless they are granted a release from the community signed by the President Coach, Team manager, or at least two out of the three. Players representing our community in any league or tournament are required to stay in the designated team area and be fully dressed and ready if called upon.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[2] </strong>If a player has any concerns, they can either talk to the coach or the team manager about your concern.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[3]</strong> Players are expected to have team spirit win lose or draw.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[4]</strong> Players are expected to be disciplined as they are a representation of our community. (Respect opponent, respect referee, etc.)</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[5]</strong> Players need to communicate with Coaches if they are running late for practice or games.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[6]</strong> Captains are expected to demonstrate leadership in the field and outside the field.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[7]</strong> Players must respect coachesâ€™ decisions, refusal to do so will lead to suspension, which can be determined by the coaching staff and captains.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[8]</strong> Team equipment must be respected and handled with care (bibs, cons, balls, jerseys, captain band).</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[9]</strong> Playing the game with joy and a practice environment should and would be positive, these are a must.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[10]</strong> Players need to show up at Practice at least 2 times a week or else at the game time, you will seat on the bench.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[11]</strong> Players need to respect their teammates and if you disrespect your teammates while on the playing field you will be suspended for 2 days and 2 games.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[12]</strong> If the Coaches tell you to leave the field and you refuse, you will be suspended for 2 days and 2 games</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[13]</strong> If the Coach tells you to play even if it is 1 minute of Remaining in the game, and you refuse to go in the game and play. You will be suspended for 2 days and 2 games</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[14]</strong> If a Player intentionally tries to injure his teammate, you will be asked to live the field.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[15]</strong> A player should not be using the F word or other curse words to a teammate opponent or officials or anything that will create tension or Incitement. You will be suspended for 2 days and 2 games</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>[16]</strong> All players should respect our non-negotiable values of RESPECT, LEADERSHIP COMMITMENT DISCIPLINE, and PASSION.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
